§§ test_02_arithmetique.jlsp
§§ Test des opérations arithmétiques

(: a 20)
(: b 7)

§§ Addition
(: somme (+ a b))
(€ "a + b =")
(€ somme)

§§ Soustraction
(: diff (- a b))
(€ "a - b =")
(€ diff)

§§ Multiplication
(: prod (* a b))
(€ "a * b =")
(€ prod)

§§ Division
(: quot (/ a b))
(€ "a / b =")
(€ quot)

§§ Opérations imbriquées : (a + b) * (a - b)
(: res (* (+ a b) (- a b)))
(€ "(a+b)*(a-b) =")
(€ res)

§§ Chaîne d'additions : 1 + 2 + 3 + 4
(: chaine (+ 1 2 3 4))
(€ "1+2+3+4 =")
(€ chaine)
